---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title='Contenido1'>
  <article
    slot='content'
    class='flex items-center justify-center max-w-screen sm:mb-4 lg:mb-4 mx-4 inset-0 bg-[#e0dddd] dark:bg-[#18191d] relative'
  >
    <div class='flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 xl:ml-8 h-screen xl:mt-0 mt-40'>
      <main class='w-full lg:w-3/4 xl:mt-20'>
        <article class='prose prose-gray mx-auto dark:prose-invert'>
          <h1
            class='text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight lg:text-5xl lg:leading-[3.5rem]'
          >
            The Joke Tax Chronicles
          </h1>
          <p class='text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400'>
            Posted on August 24, 2023
          </p>
          <img
            src='/placeholder.svg'
            alt='Placeholder image'
            class='w-full h-[200px] object-cover mb-4'
            width='300'
            height='200'
            style='aspect-ratio: 300 / 200; object-fit: cover;'
          />
          <p>
            Once upon a time, in a far-off land, there was a very lazy king who
            spent all day lounging on his throne. One day, his advisors came to
            him with a problem: the kingdom was running out of money.
          </p>
          <img
            src='/placeholder.svg'
            alt='Placeholder image'
            class='w-full h-[200px] object-cover mb-4'
            width='300'
            height='200'
            style='aspect-ratio: 300 / 200; object-fit: cover;'
          />
          <p>Jokester began sneaking into the castle in the m</p>
        </article>
      </main>
    </div>
    <aside
      class='w-full h-screen md:w-1/5 mt-8 mb-0 p-6 border-l border-black dark:border-white'
    >
      <div class='border-black'>
        <h2 class='text-lg font-semibold'>Related Products</h2>
        <div class='mt-4 space-y-4'>
          <div class='flex items-center space-x-4'>
            <img
              src='/placeholder.svg'
              alt='Product image'
              width='80'
              height='80'
              class='aspect-square object-cover'
            />
            <div class='flex-1'>
              <h3
                class='text-sm font-semibold text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]'
              >
                Product Name
              </h3>
              <p class='text-sm text-[#18191d] dark:text-[#e0dddd]'>$99.99</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='flex items-center space-x-4'>
            <img
              src='/placeholder.svg'
